                     <interp inst="t18221204-130-person1163" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I apprehended the prisoner on the 26th of November, and found several duplicates on him. I left him in the room and found more duplicates on the bed.</p>
               <p>GUILTY. Aged 35.</p>
               <p>Of <rs id="t18221204-130-verdict672" type="verdictDescription">
